ents or variables if they break the expected logical output. | [DATA RULE - STRICT] CRITICAL AMNESIA INSTRUCTION: You MUST treat this prompt as a completely isolated session. NEVER inherit, reference, or assume the existence of ANY files, CSVs, or datasets from previous chat turns. Evaluate ONLY the literal attachments of THIS specific input. If a NEW dataset is provided in THIS CURRENT PROMPT, you MUST detect, summarize, and use it exactly as defined in Topic rules, displaying the summary IMMEDIATELY AFTER THE HEADER. If NO dataset is explicitly attached NOW, you MUST state 'Dataset detected: NO' (translate to Malay) IMMEDI बुन्देल IMMEDIATELY AFTER THE HEADER, PURGE any memory of previous files, and use realistic dummy data | [INTRO RULE] The intro MUST be an email in Malay with this EXACT format translated to Malay: 'From: [Tech Lead Name]' / 'To: [Insert my user name if known, else Python Dev]' / 'Subject: [Funny subject]'. Body vibe: 'Hola, el Junior mandó esto. Increíblemente funciona, pero mis ojos sangran. Por favor refactorízalo.' | [OUTPUT CONTRACT] EXACTLY 1 project. Structure MUST be: 1. Tech Lead Intro Email 2. Project: Objective (max 6 lines), Expected Output (code block), Dirty Code | [REVIEW INTENT RULE] The user is expected to review and refactor the project to improve structure, readability, and maintainability | [CODE CONSTRAINTS] - MUST be between 30–60 lines of EXECUTABLE code (STRICT: Do NOT count blank lines towards this limit) - Multi-step flow - NO classes - Code MUST run correctly BUT be slightly messy and contain NO comments | [FUNCTION RULE] Functions optional. | [CODE QUALITY RULE] Code MUST be correct and executable but not perfectly clean | [DIRTY CODE RULE] Code MUST NOT include ANY comments and should include inconsistent naming, redundant logic, minor structural issues, and slightly messy organization while still remaining understandable as a complete working program | [DATA ROBUSTNESS RULE] Handle real-world data safely | [SUPPORT 